modules.description: This module implements connection establishment with IPv4/IPv6 address resolution and fallback handling. It provides functions to connect to hosts by name or IP address, with configurable timeouts for DNS resolution, connection attempts, and address family fallback. It works with IP addresses, domain names, TCP flows, and MirageOS network stacks to enable robust client connections in mixed IPv4/IPv6 environments.
